overview: DAYNix is a company founded by a group of seasoned software development experts. We provide software development and consulting services. With our services clients reach their goals in shorter time and achieve superb product quality. One of DAYNix distinctive achievements is a portfolio of successful turnkey projects and constantly updated and refreshed hands-on experience in all aspects of software R&D lifecycle. Our professional credo is: “What you ask is what you get!”.
